    "Name": "Kossandra Gunship",
    "Details": "A Dark Age VTOL, the Kossandra is named in honor of the founder of the Magistracy. Classified as a superheavy VTOL, the Kossandra weights 60 tons, with a top speed of just shy of 100kph. A pair of UAC/5s and 6 RL-10s give the Kossandra plenty of firepower.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar biomes.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 6/9 hexes / 180/270 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       130     36\n<b>Left</b>         115     36\n<b>Right</b>       115     36\n<b>Rear</b>         90     36\n<b>Turret</b>       25     36\n\n<b>Total</b>      475    180</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Rugged</color>",
